CustomField.formula: IF (Germination__c >= 80, "High Germination", IF (AND(Germination__c >=51, Germination__c <= 79), "Moderate Germination(Compost has some limitations, pH and/or EC)", IF (Germination__c <= 50, "Low Germination(Germination Should be repeated after 3 weeks)",NULL)))
CustomField.label: Germination Interpretation
